00:06:15.500 --> 00:06:17.080
and want to give me more?

00:06:18.390 --> 00:06:19.830
How are you so lucid?

00:06:22.250 --> 00:06:23.220
How is this possible?

00:06:23.220 --> 00:06:25.250
With a mother like you,

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:28.480
no wonder Jun Che
became a tyrant in his previous life.

00:06:28.510 --> 00:06:30.070
I've been wondering

00:06:30.280 --> 00:06:31.840
what kind of mother

00:06:31.860 --> 00:06:33.659
would cause him such suffering.

00:06:33.659 --> 00:06:35.540
Today I finally see clearly.

00:06:36.310 --> 00:06:38.360
They say even tigers don't eat their cubs,

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:40.070
but you not only devoured yours,

00:06:40.070 --> 00:06:42.000
you didn't even spit out the bones.

00:06:42.360 --> 00:06:43.510
Who are you really?

00:06:43.510 --> 00:06:45.930
Weren't you the one
who put drugs in my bath,

00:06:46.120 --> 00:06:47.920
making Jun Che confused

00:06:48.040 --> 00:06:49.510
and hallucinate?

00:06:50.430 --> 00:06:52.500
Weren't you the one
who made Sang Li control Yan Hui,

00:06:52.500 --> 00:06:53.860
having him lie in my bed

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.600
to drive a wedge between Jun Che and me?

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:56.350
Lu Yingying.

00:06:57.430 --> 00:06:58.360
Where is Jun Che?

00:06:59.720 --> 00:07:02.450
You think you're
the only one who can control him?

00:07:06.350 --> 00:07:07.480
It was all my foolishness.

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:08.870
I listened to the Saintess

00:07:08.870 --> 00:07:10.310
and controlled Yan Hui's body

00:07:10.310 --> 00:07:11.600
to pressure His Majesty.

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:13.760
She threatened you
with my brother's life.

00:07:13.760 --> 00:07:16.490
That's why
you were forced to control my brother.

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:17.390
Control?

00:07:18.750 --> 00:07:20.430
Do you still have
the Heart-Binding Poison?

00:07:20.430 --> 00:07:23.310
The Heart-Binding Poison can only
be used on one person in a lifetime.

00:07:23.310 --> 00:07:25.000
I've already used mine on Yan Hui.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:25.830
I mean

00:07:25.830 --> 00:07:27.830
a brand new Heart-Binding Poison worm.

00:07:27.830 --> 00:07:30.250
You want to control His Majesty

00:07:30.310 --> 00:07:31.720
