00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:32.360
Yes.

00:07:46.480 --> 00:07:48.080
His Majesty is unconscious.

00:07:48.159 --> 00:07:49.620
Watch over him carefully.

00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:52.770
You're the Empress?

00:07:57.750 --> 00:07:58.560
Guards!

00:07:58.870 --> 00:07:59.190
Seize her...

00:07:59.190 --> 00:08:00.250
-Freeze!
-Freeze!

00:08:01.600 --> 00:08:03.480
All your men have been captured.

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:09.480
Sang Li.

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:11.160
Don't forget

00:08:11.180 --> 00:08:12.920
your lover's life

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:14.480
is still in my hands.

00:08:21.330 --> 00:08:22.360
I see now.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:25.490
So you've been in cahoots all along.

00:08:26.100 --> 00:08:28.710
I was once deceived
by the former emperor of Daning.

00:08:28.710 --> 00:08:31.590
And now I'm being deceived by you again.

00:08:32.169 --> 00:08:34.169
People of Daning are truly cunning.

00:08:34.539 --> 00:08:36.250
You all truly deserve to die.

