00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:54.380
and forced me to bear that bastard child.

00:08:54.600 --> 00:08:56.150
How could his blood alone

00:08:56.150 --> 00:08:58.390
be enough to repay
all the humiliation I've suffered?

00:08:58.390 --> 00:09:01.060
But the common people
of Daning are innocent.

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:01.970
Innocent?

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:04.150
They enjoy the benefits of Daning.

00:09:04.150 --> 00:09:06.080
They kneel before
that bastard emperor every day.

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:07.380
How are they innocent?

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:08.840
That's absurd.

00:09:09.490 --> 00:09:10.900
What about Jun Che?

00:09:11.110 --> 00:09:12.510
Your own flesh and blood.

00:09:13.480 --> 00:09:14.720
What flesh and blood?

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:17.090
