to come out of seclusion.

00:09:35.670 --> 00:09:37.390
But your enemy is dead.

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:40.120
The resentment in your heart
is hard to dissolve.

00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:41.440
At the same time, you know

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:42.790
